    "# ☀️🌬️ Solar & Wind Energy AI Chatbot\n",
    "## Multi-Agent Debate Framework · Powered by Groq LLM\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "### 🤖 Four Specialized Agents:\n",
    "| Agent | Name | Role |\n",
    "|-------|------|------|\n",
    "| 🔆 | **Dr. Solar** | Solar PV expert — panels, efficiency, economics |\n",
    "| 💨 | **Dr. Windward** | Wind energy engineer — turbines, power curves |\n",
    "| 🔍 | **Dr. Critic** | Skeptic — catches errors, verifies calculations |\n",
    "| 🎯 | **Dr. Synthesis** | Final synthesizer — produces definitive answer |\n",
    "\n",
    "### 🔄 Debate Flow:\n",
    "```\n",
    "Question → [Topic Filter] → Round 1 (Solar + Wind answer) → Critic challenges\n",
    "         → Round 2 (Experts refine) → Critic verifies → Dr. Synthesis → FINAL ANSWER\n",
    "```\n",
    "---"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cell-md-02",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
